meanings: Chemical Formula C22H22O2. A chemical structure of a molecule includes the arrangement of atoms and the chemical bonds that hold the atoms together. An emotion that is stronger than <3
The Potterhead's version of 'I love you'. Seven, being the most powerful magical number in the Harry Potter series, is used as a substitute for the number three.
